I"U<p>ElementControl is a game where you have to defend the top of a mountain from enemies using the elements: water, lava, earth and air.</p>

<p>I made this game when I was 14 years old for the <a href="https://youtub.o">LetsGameDev Game++</a> community challenge to develop a game with pre-defined assets only.</p>

<p>The video is still online:</p>

